{"tid":1632350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［裝修最強招數］重要！裝修佬入！！和理非都入！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:57:42.000Z","uid":202994,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55ea712de1f9c4cba10d0e0b34bec9dfad86b3d7","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:41:27.000Z","msg":"最近大家啲裝修都太快 文宣煲唔切<br />\n好多人都真係蠢唔係扮咁唔知大家做緊乜 覺得手足搞破壞 會反感<br />\n有見及此 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家會係裝修個時同我將文宣貼出黎 解釋點解要搞 再唔係就噴（中資/黑社會等等）</span></span><br />\n班和理非見到有裝修佬做野又唔敢拆埋一份 <br />\n你就好好發揮你既功用 務求全港被裝修既鋪都有文宣係個到解釋 <br />\n如果可以好似之前雜總 柒婆個樣咁遍地開花就最好<br />\n打左幾日 要大大力咁做下文宣啦各位 唔好裝修到上晒腦<br />\n記住四點 <strong>黑裝修 <span style=\"color: red;\">紅裝飾</span> <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"> 藍罷買</span></strong> <span style=\"color: gold;\">黃幫襯</span></strong>！！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有少少題外話 唔知手足最近係咪好大壓力<br />\n屌人影相態度差到以為自己見到黑社會 <br />\n認真 大家出黎好好保護自己 遮好啲 影到你都唔知你乜水<br />\n再講 好多人八掛影下 唔洗屌得咁落力 真係會反感<br />\n敵人多一個都嫌多！<br />\n仲有 對付影相個啲慳少少力 唔洗下下召喚神獸既<br />\n<br />\n同埋 召喚神獸都可以搵啲和理非做解釋！ 唔該大家帶多啲紙同筆出街 神獸出現寫幾隻字俾人影到 例如：出手傷人/持械 影相呢啲理由送生日歌送佢走或者好聲氣少少叫佢del就算 我地既敵人從來都係政府 黑警 唔好錯晒focus<br />\n<br />\n最後 文宣呢家野大家實有好多 放少少出黎 希望接下來幾日會見到呢啲文宣都遍地開心<br />\n歡迎理由討論 不完美但可接受 需要改善<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n1014就係人權法 煲翻大佢呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP0MNJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP0MNJd.jpg&h=20c042cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66w8gBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66w8gBz.jpg&h=9d82f2da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuR8gBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuR8gBz.jpg&h=6cc8dc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NuQg9WA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuQg9WA.jpg&h=c1940bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPWsw9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPWsw9W.jpg&h=00f73c84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"962bb6b61d901e10b8239f3e9bc9fd8803a907c1","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"06b66c69e5fd79b450eab9c21cf8520f98220fff","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"02113a715040a9741ba08d75c1aec07ab02143ca","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"6a516035a3a6a9bad9211c71674a3a7aac235128","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:47.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"df0793d9d3ef58fe635559bc1534752b3a25f706","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"24aee5416f3735fdd59f03f6ccce1386f365d607","tid":1632350,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"記住勇做完野由和掩護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"451b442cf41b2a14443b3e7b09b6898d0e16be88","tid":1632350,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"極有用文宣！印！"},{"pid":"1e1466d9a5d60f4f54fac0cab396fac0e5d65f59","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"7326e588ce0a430e48f7f47f8d6a72143fe5f7bd","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"e9d5805992ae30cb130ebf16dc8812de598fb871","tid":1632350,"uid":202994,"